OL,3,CSpring Clean: Keep, Chuck or Cash In?
OL,5,FJanet, 81, from Greater Manchester
OL,6,Fknows all too well how clutter can
OL,7,Faccumulate after illness left her
OL,8,Fstruggling to manage the possessions
OL,9,Fin her home. Although she downsized to
OL,10,Fa smaller bungalow in her mid-70s, she
OL,11,Ffound it difficult to part with items
OL,12,Fthat carried memories. She now
OL,13,Freceives regular support from
OL,14,Fprofessional declutterer Georgina
OL,15,FBurdett, who helps her sort through
OL,16,Fbelongings, decide what to keep,
OL,17,Fdonate or sell.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
