OL,3,CSpring Clean: Keep, Chuck or Cash In?
OL,5,FFor Swedish-born interior designer
OL,6,FMarie MacDowall, it's best to start
OL,7,Fthe process of decluttering earlier in
OL,8,Flife. Following the Scandinavian
OL,9,Fpractice of 'death cleaning', Marie
OL,10,Fgradually sorted through possessions
OL,11,Fwhen she turned 60. Five years on,
OL,12,FMarie keeps her home deliberately
OL,13,Fminimalist, following a simple rule of
OL,14,Fletting something go whenever she buys
OL,15,Fsomething new.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
