CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773414683
OL,3,CSpring Clean: Keep, Chuck or Cash In?
OL,5,F"Swedish death cleaning is an act of
OL,6,Flove. I would say if you start
OL,7,Fsometime in your 60s, you get time to
OL,8,Fconsider what is important. You go
OL,9,Fthrough all your possessions. Start
OL,10,Fasking yourself these questions: Do I
OL,11,Fneed it? Have I used it for the last
OL,12,F10 years or the last 2 years? Will I
OL,13,Fuse it again?"
OL,15,F` Marie MacDowall
OL,26,@mD@AOUuD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
