OL,3,CSpring Clean: Keep, Chuck or Cash In?
OL,5,FIt turns out many of us may be sitting
OL,6,Fon valuable items without realising
OL,7,Fit. According to Scott Butler of
OL,8,FMaterial Focus, which runs the Recycle
OL,9,FYour Electricals campaign, many
OL,10,Fhouseholds are sitting on valuable
OL,11,Fclutter in the form of unused gadgets
OL,12,Fand cables, which often collect in a
OL,13,F'drawer of doom'. He estimates the
OL,14,Faverage home could hold hundreds of
OL,15,Fpounds' worth of sellable electronics.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
